message.body: Hi! I heard you and Julie might get dinner- if you want company, let me know! No pressure, because either way I will see you on 12/30 at Barnes!? I'll look into tickets tonight
Awesome! And yes, dinner on Sunday, time tbd. You in?
My bus on Tues leaves Chinatown at 4:30 (I think the Barnes closes before then anyway)
Oh awesome yes. I misunderstood and thought you had dinner planned for tonight
Was also going to try to meet up with a friend for late breakfast/early lunch on tue, but I'll try to see if she can reschedule so we won't be rushed!
Oh no worries- Julie said you were in Philly tonight and all having dinner and invited me and I just didn't want her to think I ditched
Oh – I'm not in Philly yet :P still working this week
Bc I ditched her bday accidentally without realizing it!!
It's all good!! See you next week!!!
Haha I'm preeeetty sure Julie knows I'm not there but maybe I should doublecheck!
Lol it might have been a mistranslation of dates
